CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 10, 1952, pg. 11, reads: "Happy Birthday! - Having fun at a birthday party which feted Mrs. Ida Royal were these happy folk. Front row: Lindy Horton, Morland Townes, Ida Royal, Bobby Horton and Ida Mae Royal. Back row are Lillian Townes, Martha Davis, Shepard Royal, Billy Maxwell, Blanche Horton, Maud Beaner and Louise Horton. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Lindy Horton, Morland Townes, Ida Royal, Bobby Horton, Ida Mae Royal, Lillian Townes, Martha Davis, Shepard Royal, Billy Maxwell, Blanche Horton, Maud Bean, and Louise Horton wearing party hats at birthday party for Ida Royal, another version
